B.a9I=new A.k_("Fibrillations & Positive Sharp Waves","These represent spontaneous muscle fiber discharges, meaning the fiber lost its nerve supply. This is your classic hallmark of active denervation seen in radiculopathy, neuropathy, or motor neuron disease.","jjUZMf8_B1k",B.a2j)
