B.a9K=new A.k_("Myokymic Discharges","Think of an entire motor unit bursting repetitively. It has a very distinct 'marching soldiers' cadence. If you see this in the limbs, strongly consider radiation injury. If you see it in the face, consider MS or a brainstem glioma.","ZClcikXOOaU",B.a_a)
B.Me=new A.cq("The Sound","A 'dive bomber' or a 'revving motorcycle engine'.")
