B.M1=new A.cq("The Rate","Typically 20-150Hz. Remember, the rate actively changes.")
B.M6=new A.cq("Key Pathology","Myotonic dystrophy, myotonia congenita, paramyotonia congenita, and occasionally hyperkalemic periodic paralysis.")
