B.a9G=new A.k_("Myotonic Discharges","The classic 'dive bomber.' This is an unstable muscle fiber membrane that repetitively discharges. The defining feature is that it waxes and wanes in both frequency and amplitude.","X29z-QTi0tM",B.YN)
B.Mb=new A.cq("The Sound","Random, large, distant 'pops'. Think of 'corn popping' slowly in a microwave.")
B.Mf=new A.cq("The Look","A normal-looking (or reinnervated) MUAP that fires spontaneously.")
B.M7=new A.cq("The Rate","Very slow and highly irregular (0.1-10Hz).")
