B.axi=new A.oq("What is the primary pathological difference between demyelinating and axonal neuropathies?",B.ZX,0,"Demyelinating neuropathies damage Schwann cells (myelin), slowing signals. Axonal neuropathies involve degeneration of the axon itself, reducing amplitudes.")
