ae7=A.cg("No visible atrophy (acute onset).","Mild deep tenderness in the proximal volar forearm.",v4,v3,"STRICTLY NORMAL throughout the median, ulnar, and radial distributions. No palmar or digital numbness.","Negative 'OK' sign (Patient's thumb and index finger meet in a flat 'pincer' position rather than a circle due to lack of distal IP/DIP flexion).","Right Flexor Pollicis Longus (FPL) 2/5, Flexor Digitorum Profundus (FDP) of index finger 2/5. Normal strength in Pronator Teres, FCR, and APB (Hand intrinsics). Normal strength in FDP of 4th and 5th digits (Ulnar).")
